<tr id="L12"><td><a href="#L12">12</a></td><td>SOLOK:  Of course I do. But humans are often irked by such precision. Especially the more emotional humans. Our repair list. I understand you were recently honoured with the Christopher Pike Medal for Valour. Congratulations.</td></tr>

