<tr id="L52"><td><a href="#L52">52</a></td><td>EZRI:  Right, except it's bases loaded. Now, what's a Fancy Dan?</td></tr>

<tr id="L53"><td><a href="#L53">53</a></td><td>O'BRIEN:  A what?</td></tr>

<tr id="L54"><td><a href="#L54">54</a></td><td>BASHIR:  You're making that up.</td></tr>

